object.script:
i=input o=output p=property s=screen IB=i.getBool IN=i.getNumber OB=o.setBool ON=o.setNumber PN=p.getNumber Color=s.setColor Text=s.drawText m=math abs=m.abs S=m.sin C=m.cos T=m.tan AS=m.asin AT=m.atan e=m.exp(1) pi=m.pi pi2=2*pi tX,tY,tA=0,0,0 cX,cY,cA=0,0,0 vX,vY,vA=0,0,0 cH,cV=0,0 acq=false tracking=false acqTime=0 Vnew=function(_x,_y,_z) local obj={} obj.x=_x obj.y=_y obj.z=_z return obj end VAdd=function(a,b) local obj={} obj.x=a.x+b.x obj.y=a.y+b.y obj.z=a.z+b.z return obj end VInv=function(a) local obj={} obj.x=-a.x obj.y=-a.y obj.z=-a.z return obj end QConjugate=function(q) local obj={} obj.x=-q.x obj.y=-q.y obj.z=-q.z obj.w=q.w return obj end QMul=function(a,b) local obj={} obj.x=a.w*b.x-a.z*b.y+a.y*b.z+a.x*b.w obj.y=a.z*b.x+a.w*b.y-a.x*b.z+a.y*b.w obj.z=-a.y*b.x+a.x*b.y+a.w*b.z+a.z*b.w obj.w=-a.x*b.x-a.y*b.y-a.z*b.z+a.w*b.w return obj end QMulVec=function(q, v) local N1=q.x*2 local N2=q.y*2 local N3=q.z*2 local N4=q.x*N1 local N5=q.y*N2 local N6=q.z*N3 local N7=q.x*N2 local N8=q.x*N3 local N9=q.y*N3 local N10=q.w*N1 local N11=q.w*N2 local N12=q.w*N3 local obj={} obj.x=(((1-(N5+N6))*v.x)+((N7-N12)*v.y))+((N8+N11)*v.z) obj.y=(((N7+N12)*v.x)+((1-(N4+N6))*v.y))+((N9-N10)*v.z) obj.z=(((N8-N11)*v.x)+((N9+N10)*v.y))+((1-(N4+N5))*v.z) return obj end QtoEulerZXY=function(q) local sx=2*q.y*q.z+2*q.x*q.w; local locked=abs(sx) > 0.99999; local obj={} if locked then obj.x=AS(sx) obj.y=0 obj.z=AT(2*q.x*q.y+2*q.z*q.w, 2*q.w*q.w+2*q.x*q.x-1) else obj.x=AS(sx) obj.y=AT(-(2*q.x*q.z-2*q.y*q.w), 2*q.w*q.w+2*q.z*q.z-1) obj.z=AT(-(2*q.x*q.y-2*q.z*q.w), 2*q.w*q.w+2*q.y*q.y-1) end return obj end QfromEulerZXY=function(e) local cx=C(0.5*e.x) local sx=S(0.5*e.x) local cy=C(0.5*e.y) local sy=S(0.5*e.y) local cz=C(0.5*e.z) local sz=S(0.5*e.z) local obj={} obj.x=-cx*sy*sz+sx*cy*cz obj.y=cx*sy*cz+sx*cy*sz obj.z=sx*sy*cz+cx*cy*sz obj.w=-sx*sy*sz+cx*cy*cz return obj end function QfromSensor(ft,rt,fc) local phi=fc local theta=ft local psi=AS(S(-rt*pi2)/S((0.25-ft)*pi2)) return QfromEulerZXY(Vnew(theta*pi2,phi*pi2,psi)) end function localFromRadar(d,a,e) local y=d*S(e) local w=d*C(e) local x=w*S(a) local z=w*C(a) return Vnew(x,y,z) end function Dist2(x,y) return m.sqrt(x*x+y*y) end function Distf(x,y,z) return x*x+y*y+z*z end function onTick() gpsX=IN(4) gpsY=IN(8) gpsA=IN(12) if IB(9) then tracking=not tracking and IB(1) acq=false if tracking and IB(1) then AAPos=QMulVec(QConjugate(QR),localFromRadar(IN(1),IN(2)*pi2,IN(3)*pi2)) cX=AAPos.x+gpsX cY=AAPos.z+gpsY cA=AAPos.y+gpsA end end if IB(10) then cX=IN(16) cY=IN(20) cA=IN(24) acq=true tracking=false end lock=false lockNum=0 if IB(1) then QR=QfromSensor(IN(25),IN(26),IN(27)) maxDist=10000 tempX,tempY,tempA=0,0,0 for i=1,6 do AAPos=QMulVec(QConjugate(QR),localFromRadar(IN(i*4-3),IN(i*4-2)*pi2,IN(i*4-1)*pi2)) vX=AAPos.x+gpsX vY=AAPos.z+gpsY vA=AAPos.y+gpsA errorDist=Distf(cX-vX,cY-vY,cA-vA) if errorDist < maxDist then lock=true tempX=vX tempY=vY tempA=vA lockNum=i maxDist=errorDist end end
if lock then if acq then acq=false tracking=true elseif tracking then cX=tempX cY=tempY cA=tempA end end end
if acq or tracking then QB=QfromSensor(IN(29),IN(30),IN(31),IN(32)) turretQ=QfromEulerZXY(Vnew(AT(cA-gpsA,Dist2(cX-gpsX,cY-gpsY)),AT(cY-gpsY,cX-gpsX)-pi/2,0)) turretQ=QMul(turretQ,QConjugate(QB)) turretE=QtoEulerZXY(turretQ) cH=Dist2(cX-gpsX,cY-gpsY) ON(5,turretE.y/pi2) ON(6,turretE.x*4/pi2) end
OB(1,lock) OB(2,acq) OB(3,tracking) OB(4,acq or tracking) ON(1,cX) ON(2,cY) ON(3,cA) ON(4,0) ON(7,cH) ON(8,lockNum) end
function onDraw() w=s.getWidth() h=s.getHeight()
Text(2,2,string.format("X: %5.0f",cX)) Text(2,8,string.format("Y: %5.0f",cY)) Text(2,14,string.format("Alt: %5.0f",cA)) Text(2,20,string.format("HDist: %5.0f",cH))
if tracking then Text(2,26,"tracking") elseif acq then Text(2,26,"acquiring") else Text(2,26,"standing by") end end

i=input o=output p=property s=screen m=math IB=i.getBool IN=i.getNumber OB=o.setBool ON=o.setNumber PN=p.getNumber Color=s.setColor Text=s.drawText Line=s.drawLine Rect=s.drawRect RectF=s.drawRect
S=m.sin C=m.cos pi=m.pi pi2=pi*2
w,h,cX,cY=0,0,0,0 gX,gY,bC,tC,rX,rY,tX,tY=0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0 searching,tracking,fix=false,false,true
LSize=PN('Lock Shape Size') rFovX=PN('Radar FoV X') rFovY=PN('Radar FoV Y')
targetFound={false,false,false,false,false,false,false,false} targetAzi={0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0} targetElv={0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0}
lock=false pLock=false lockNum=0 azi=0 elv=0 fov=0.5
t_Tt=PN('tau/T+tau')
function lerp(a,b,t) return a * (1-t) + b * t end
function onTick()
fov=lerp(2.2,0.025,IN(4))/pi2
-- hontoha -(T/T+2tau) nanodakeredo betsuni...
for i=1,8 do targetFound[i]=IB(i) targetAzi[i]=IN(i*4-2) targetElv[i]=IN(i*4-1) end
lockNum=IN(8) lock=lockNum~=0 if lock then if pLock then azi=t_Tt*azi+(1-t_Tt)*IN(lockNum*4-2) elv=t_Tt*elv+(1-t_Tt)*IN(lockNum*4-1) else azi=IN(lockNum*4-2) elv=IN(lockNum*4-1) end end pLock=lock
end
function onDraw() w = s.getWidth() h = s.getHeight()
Color(0,0,0,127)
Rect((w-rFovX*w/fov)/2,(h-rFovY*h/fov)/2,rFovX*w/fov,rFovY*h/fov)
Color(255,255,255,127) for j=1,8 do if targetFound[j] and j~=lockNum then Rect((w-LSize)/2+targetAzi[j]*w/fov,(h-LSize)/2-targetElv[j]*h/fov,LSize,LSize) end end
Color(255,0,0) if lockNum~=0 then Rect((w-LSize)/2+azi*w/fov,(h-LSize)/2-elv*h/fov,LSize,LSize) end end

object.script:
i=input o=output p=property IB=i.getBool IN=i.getNumber OB=o.setBool ON=o.setNumber PB=p.getBool PN=p.getNumber m=math abs=m.abs S=m.sin C=m.cos T=m.tan AS=m.asin AT=m.atan e=m.exp(1) pi=m.pi pi2=2*pi
Vnew=function(_x,_y,_z) local obj={} obj.x=_x obj.y=_y obj.z=_z return obj end VAdd=function(a,b) local obj={} obj.x=a.x+b.x obj.y=a.y+b.y obj.z=a.z+b.z return obj end VInv=function(a) local obj={} obj.x=-a.x obj.y=-a.y obj.z=-a.z return obj end
QConjugate=function(q) local obj={} obj.x=-q.x obj.y=-q.y obj.z=-q.z obj.w=q.w return obj end
QMul=function(a,b) local obj={} obj.x=a.w*b.x-a.z*b.y+a.y*b.z+a.x*b.w obj.y=a.z*b.x+a.w*b.y-a.x*b.z+a.y*b.w obj.z=-a.y*b.x+a.x*b.y+a.w*b.z+a.z*b.w obj.w=-a.x*b.x-a.y*b.y-a.z*b.z+a.w*b.w return obj end
QMulVec=function(q, v) local N1=q.x*2 local N2=q.y*2 local N3=q.z*2 local N4=q.x*N1 local N5=q.y*N2 local N6=q.z*N3 local N7=q.x*N2 local N8=q.x*N3 local N9=q.y*N3 local N10=q.w*N1 local N11=q.w*N2 local N12=q.w*N3
local obj={} obj.x=(((1-(N5+N6))*v.x)+((N7-N12)*v.y))+((N8+N11)*v.z) obj.y=(((N7+N12)*v.x)+((1-(N4+N6))*v.y))+((N9-N10)*v.z) obj.z=(((N8-N11)*v.x)+((N9+N10)*v.y))+((1-(N4+N5))*v.z) return obj end
QtoEulerYXZ=function(q) local sx=-(2*q.y*q.z-2*q.x*q.w); local locked=abs(sx) > 0.99999; local obj={} if locked then obj.x=AS(sx) obj.y=AT(2*q.x*q.z+2*q.y*q.w,2*q.w*q.w+2*q.z*q.z-1) obj.z=AT(2*q.x*q.y+2*q.z*q.w,2*q.w*q.w+2*q.y*q.y-1) else obj.x=AS(sx) obj.y=AT(-(2*q.x*q.z-2*q.y*q.w),2*q.w*q.w+2*q.x*q.x-1) obj.z=0 end return obj end
QtoEulerZXY=function(q) local sx=2*q.y*q.z+2*q.x*q.w; local locked=abs(sx) > 0.99999; local obj={} if locked then obj.x=AS(sx) obj.y=0 obj.z=AT(2*q.x*q.y+2*q.z*q.w, 2*q.w*q.w+2*q.x*q.x-1) else obj.x=AS(sx) obj.y=AT(-(2*q.x*q.z-2*q.y*q.w), 2*q.w*q.w+2*q.z*q.z-1) obj.z=AT(-(2*q.x*q.y-2*q.z*q.w), 2*q.w*q.w+2*q.y*q.y-1) end return obj end
QfromEulerZXY=function(e) local cx=C(0.5*e.x) local sx=S(0.5*e.x) local cy=C(0.5*e.y) local sy=S(0.5*e.y) local cz=C(0.5*e.z) local sz=S(0.5*e.z) local obj={} obj.x=-cx*sy*sz+sx*cy*cz obj.y=cx*sy*cz+sx*cy*sz obj.z=sx*sy*cz+cx*cy*sz obj.w=-sx*sy*sz+cx*cy*cz return obj end
function localFromRadar(d,a,e) local y=d*S(e) local w=d*C(e) local x=w*S(a) local z=w*C(a) return Vnew(x,y,z) end
function QfromSensor(ft,rt,fc) local phi=fc local theta=ft local psi=AS(S(-rt*pi2)/S((0.25-ft)*pi2)) return QfromEulerZXY(Vnew(theta*pi2,phi*pi2,psi)) end function onTick()
if true then
gpsX=IN(4) gpsY=IN(8) gpsA=IN(12)
targetX=IN(29)-gpsX targetY=IN(30)-gpsY targetA=IN(31)-gpsA
q=QfromSensor(IN(16),IN(20),IN(24))
for i=1,7 do local detected = IB(i) if detected then local localPos = localFromRadar(IN(4*i-3),IN(4*i-2)*pi2,IN(4*i-1)*pi2) local AAPos = QMulVec(QConjugate(q),localPos) ON(3*i+9,gpsX + AAPos.x) ON(3*i+10,gpsY + AAPos.z) ON(3*i+11,gpsA + AAPos.y) end OB(i,detected) end end
end

i=input o=output p=property t=table s=screen m=math IB=i.getBool IN=i.getNumber OB=o.setBool ON=o.setNumber PB=p.getBool PN=p.getNumber TI=t.insert TR=t.remove Color=s.setColor Text=s.drawText Line=s.drawLine Rect=s.drawRect RectF=s.drawRectF Circle=s.drawCircle CircleF=s.drawCircleF TriF=s.drawTriangleF
S=m.sin C=m.cos pi=m.pi pi2=pi*2
w,h,cX,cY=0,0,0,0 gX,gY,bC,tC,rX,rY,tX,tY=0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0 pPressed,searching,acquiring,tracking,fix=false,false,false,false,true
aX,aY,aA=0,0,0
zoom=10 searchRange=PN('Search Radar Range') missileRange=PN('Missile Range')
targets={} displayed={}
tgmax=100 tgMinDist=2500
function onTick() tX=IN(1) tY=IN(2) gX=IN(3) gY=IN(4) bC=IN(5)*pi2 tC=IN(6)*pi2 rC=IN(7)*pi2-tC-pi/2 rX=IN(8) rY=IN(9)
pressed=IB(9) searching=IB(10) tracking=IB(11)
OB(1,false)
if pressed then if not pPressed then
if Cursor(1,h-9,8,h-1) then fix=true elseif Cursor(1,1,8,8) then zoom=m.max(zoom/1.5,0.1) elseif Cursor(1,9,8,16) then zoom=m.min(zoom*1.5,50) else for k=1,#displayed do if Cursor(displayed[k].x-3,displayed[k].y-3,displayed[k].x+3,displayed[k].y+3) then aX,aY,aA=targets[displayed[k].i].x,targets[displayed[k].i].y,targets[displayed[k].i].a ON(1,aX) ON(2,aY) ON(3,aA) OB(1,true) break end end end elseif Cursor(w/2-32,h/2-32,w/2+32,h/2+32) then fix=false cX,cY=cX+(tX-w/2)*zoom*32/w,cY+(h/2-tY)*zoom*32/h end end
if searching then for i=1,7 do if IB(i) and #targets<tgmax then x,y,a=IN(3*i+9),IN(3*i+10),IN(3*i+11) new=true
for j=1,#targets do if Distf(targets[j].x-x,targets[j].y-y,targets[j].a-a) < tgMinDist then new=false break end end
if new then target={} target.x=x target.y=y target.a=a target.t=200 TI(targets,target) end else break end end for l=#targets,1,-1 do timer=targets[l].t targets[l].t=timer-1 if timer<15 then TR(targets,l) end end end
if fix then cX,cY=gX,gY end
pPressed = pressed end
function Distf(x,y,z) return x*x+y*y+z*z end function Cursor(lX,lY,uX,uY) return tX>lX and tX<uX and tY>lY and tY<uY end
function onDraw() w = s.getWidth() h = s.getHeight()
s.setMapColorOcean(5,5,5) s.setMapColorShallows(10,10,10) s.setMapColorLand(30,30,30) s.setMapColorGrass(20,20,20) s.setMapColorSand(40,40,40) s.setMapColorSnow(50,50,50)
s.drawMap(cX,cY,zoom) vX,vY=map.mapToScreen(cX, cY, zoom, w, h, gX, gY)
displayed={}
-- render radar range if searching then searchCircle=searchRange*w/(zoom*1000) Color(0,0,255,15) CircleF(vX,vY,searchCircle) Color(0,0,255) Circle(vX,vY,searchCircle) Line(vX,vY,searchCircle*C(rC)+vX,searchCircle*S(rC)+vY)

i,o,p,m=input,output,property,math IB,IN,OB,ON,PN,PB=i.getBool,i.getNumber,o.setBool,o.setNumber,p.getNumber,p.getBool S,C,T,AS,AT,pi,pi2=m.sin,m.cos,m.tan,m.asin,m.atan,m.pi,2*m.pi
tx,ty,ta=0,0,0 ltx,lty,lta=0,0,0 lrx,lry,lra=0,0,0 lgx,lgy,lga=0,0,0
finYaw,finPitch=0,0
eta=100 found=0 yawRate,pitchRate,yawAcc,pitchAcc=0,0,0,0 lyawRate,lpitchRate,lyawAcc,lpitchAcc=0,0,0,0 lpYaw,lpPitch,lpDist=0,0,0 lvSpeed=0
lMode=PN('Launch Mode') gMode=PN('Guidance Mode') turn=lMode<2 climb=lMode<1 radio=gMode<2 radar=gMode>0
navY=PN("Yaw navigation constant") or 5 navP=PN("Pitch navigation constant") or 5 navR=PN('Radar navigation constant') or 0.1
trimI=PN('Trim Init') trimA=PN('Trim Alpha') trimS=PN('Max Speed(m/s)') trimD=PN('Trim Direction')
LPF=PB('LPF') lpfT=PN('LPF T') lpfTau=PN('LPF Tau')*2 lpfIn=lpfT/(lpfT+lpfTau) lpfOut=(lpfT-lpfTau)/(lpfT+lpfTau)
function Dist2(x,y) return Dist3(x,y,0) end function Dist3(x,y,z) return m.sqrt(x*x+y*y+z*z) end function Clamp(x,min,max) return m.min(m.max(x,min),max) end
function onTick()
gx,gy,ga=IN(1),IN(2),IN(3) fTilt=IN(4) rTilt=IN(5) rx,ry,ra,rb=IN(6),IN(7),IN(8),IN(9) rAzi=IN(10) rElv=IN(11) launched=IN(12)>0
received=rx~=0 and ry~=0
if received then if LPF then tx=lpfIn*(rx+lrx)-lpfOut*ltx ty=lpfIn*(ry+lry)-lpfOut*lty ta=lpfIn*(ra+lra)-lpfOut*lta else tx,ty,ta=rx,ry,ra end end
--LOS px,py,pa=tx-gx,ty-gy,ta-ga pDist=Dist3(px,py,pa) pYaw=AT(px,py) pPitch=AT(pa,Dist2(px,py))
-- Velocity of missile vx,vy,va=gx-lgx,gy-lgy,ga-lga vYaw=AT(vx,vy) vPitch=AT(va,Dist2(vx,vy)) vSpeed=Dist3(vx,vy,va)*60 vAccel=(vSpeed-lvSpeed)*60 debug.log(vSpeed)
dYaw=(pYaw-vYaw+pi)%pi2-pi dPitch=pPitch-vPitch
if received then relSpeed=(lpDist-pDist)*60 yawRate=pYaw-lpYaw pitchRate=pPitch-lpPitch yawAcc=(yawRate-lyawRate) pitchAcc=(pitchRate-lpitchRate) yawAccAcc=(yawAcc-lyawAcc) pitchAccAcc=(pitchAcc-lpitchAcc) eta=pDist/relSpeed finYaw=yawRate*m.abs(relSpeed)+yawAccAcc*eta*5+yawAcc*eta^2 finPitch=pitchRate*m.abs(relSpeed)+pitchAccAcc*eta*5+pitchAcc*eta^2 end
if true or launched then Yaw=0 Pitch=0 if radio and tx ~= 0 and ty ~= 0 then roll=AS(S(rTilt*pi2)/C(fTilt*pi2)) if relSpeed>20 then cYaw=finYaw*navY*Clamp(eta/6,0.3,1) cPitch=finPitch*navP*Clamp(eta/6,0.3,1)
Yaw=C(roll)*cYaw+S(roll)*cPitch Pitch=C(roll)*cPitch-S(roll)*cYaw
else Yaw=C(roll)*dYaw+S(roll)*dPitch Pitch=C(roll)*dPitch-S(roll)*dYaw end end if climb then Yaw=0 Pitch=0 if ra~=0 then climb=ga<ra*0.5 end elseif turn then Yaw=S(rb*pi2)*2 Pitch=-C(rb*pi2)*2 if pPitch ~= 0 then turn=pPitch/pi2+0.05<fTilt end end if radar and rAzi ~= 0 or rElv ~= 0 then found=3 end if found>0 then Yaw=rAzi*navR Pitch=rElv*navR found=found-1 end
trim=trimI+trimA*(vSpeed/trimS) trimY=(trimD%2)*(trimD-2)*trim trimP=((trimD+1)%2)*(trimD-1)*trim ON(1,Yaw+trimY) ON(2,Pitch+trimP) end
ltx,lty,lta=tx,ty,ta lrx,lry,lra=rx,ry,ra lgx,lgy,lga=gx,gy,ga lpYaw,lpPitch,lpDist=pYaw,pPitch,pDist lyawRate,lpitchRate,lyawAcc,lpitchAcc=yawRate,pitchRate,yawAcc,pitchAcc lvSpeed=vSpeed end
